assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再有一部分有錢有時間既可能加多個歐洲<br />\n香港人鐘意去旅行但究極偏食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:31:58.000Z","msg":"係，識唔少人旅行只會去日韓台泰嘅大城市，仲識過一個朋友去旅行一定要揀個目的地似香港先會去<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔係受限於budget, 而係真心適應唔到同香港差別太大嘅文化同生活方式"},{"pid":"94c5d83ad51212cb5d98faf7e2d88f1df84ecdc1","tid":2426401,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77c2c24b4b6a2b9a647fbe3599dc3c4f28722bd1","tid":2426401,"uid":266131,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"識人未離開過香港...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"幾多歲先？"},{"pid":"33dd417960577051eca3d6f0cc22771d6fa8f84d","tid":2426401,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feef6518a26b0acdb8cc2f0f148bea66ba28257c","tid":2426401,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"888666b4b4e36c30ac0811eb79f3eaa79c0f5106","tid":2426401,"uid":27568,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"成日話要衝出亞洲<br />\n但最遠都係去阿聯酋,算係西亞<br />\n<br />\n台灣日本太吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連泰國韓國都無去過"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"阿拉伯半島都計入亞洲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:58:23.000Z","msg":"睇多啲世界地圖啦"},{"pid":"0c9324cff4d63465b34a9de956e4d85daaf303a7","tid":2426401,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T03:08:04.000Z","msg":"睇完啲回覆，想知樓主心目中嘅「東亞」係咪一般定義嘅「東亞」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d04ec9b0c3f0b4feb74a0531d6805c9cc8ec562","tid":2426401,"uid":353851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T04:50:20.000Z","msg":"要衝出亞洲最大阻力係唔夠假期，可以連放十日以上嘅機會唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢反而唔係太大問題，淡季肯花時間格價肯轉機，可以好平就去到歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但識唔少人有錢有時間都係不斷loop日韓台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，連honeymoon都仲係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然日韓台各自有佢哋相當吸引嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但去過一次歐洲，真心覺得開拓咗另一個平衡時空，係去幾多次日韓台都唔會有嘅味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以之前幾年都經常向朋友推介去歐遊，特別係鍾意睇英超嘅單身男性朋友，襯一個人自由自在，去心愛嘅球會潮聖都好吖，但無乜人聽我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13a61d4de4441102ad84cc4ede1ab958e57cfa6","tid":2426401,"uid":342282,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"澳洲算唔算離開過亞洲？<br />\n主要唔係無錢，係香港打工仔無咁長大假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbafa35f1ed7b1a4c123fc8e8f92624c5f5fad4","tid":2426401,"uid":37672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b13a61d4de4441102ad84cc4ede1ab958e57cfa6","tid":2426401,"uid":342282,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"澳洲算唔算離開過亞洲？<br />\n主要唔係無錢，係香港打工仔無咁長大假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:05:29.000Z","msg":"大洋洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e159a363a31c44f7a50c12c61ddd1a59bbeadc68","tid":2426401,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77c2c24b4b6a2b9a647fbe3599dc3c4f28722bd1","tid":2426401,"uid":266131,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"識人未離開過香港...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"渣㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}